      "value": {
        "latex": "We want to separate the plane into to half planes. One can consider the red line defined by $y=5x/8+1/2$ that is $5x-8y+4 = 0$ or another line which separates as well, for example $5x-8y=0$.  So this perceptron can fit to this problem.\n\t\n\t\n\t\\begin{center}\n\t\t__TIKZ_3cab94da-5888-4250-b220-477eec9131c6__  \n\t\\end{center}",
